dhabaani/> |- | 2010 !scope="row"| ''[[Jinni (film)|Jinni]]'' | Spell-maker | Special appearance | style="text-align: center;"| <ref name=Jinni/> |- | 2011 !scope="row"| ''[[Laelaa]]'' | Ahamma | Also the director, producer and writer | style="text-align: center;"| <ref name=Laelaa/> |- | 2019 !scope="row"| ''[[Kaaku?]]'' | Ayyoob | | style="text-align: center;"| <ref>{{cite news |url=https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/58698 |title=horror film Kaaku to release on 24 September |language=Divehi |work=Mihaaru |date=26 July 2019 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200818160759/https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/58698 |url-status=live |archivedate=18 August 2020 |accessdate=18 August 2020 |df=dmy-all }}</ref> |- | 2021 !scope="row"|''[[Kos Gina Mistake]]'' | Hamza | | style="text-align:center;"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/64669 |title=Theatrical release of KGM delayed |work=Mihaaru |language=Divehi |last=Adhushan |first=Ahmed |date=16 November 2019 |archiveurl=https://archive.vn/wip/EI0zd |url-status=live |archivedate=10 September 2020 |accessdate=10 September 2020 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- |}
===Television=== {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" |- style="background:#ccc; text-align:center;" !scope="col"| Year !scope="col"| Title !scope="col"| Role !scope="col"| Notes ! scope="col" class="unsortable" | {{Tooltip|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}} |- | 1994 !scope="row"| ''Inthizaaru'' | | | style="text-align: center;"| |- | 1998 !scope="row"| ''Un'hoo Thakuraa'' | | | style="text-align: center;"| |- | 2000 !scope="row"| ''Kashithanmathi'' | | | style="text-align: center;"| |- | 2008 !scope="row"| ''[[Soora]]'' | Fuwad | Recurring role | style="text-align: center;"|<ref name=soora>{{cite news|url=https://dho.mv/music/28773?ref=mhr-home |title=Kuda Ibbe's playlist of Best 10 |work=Dho? |date=18 January 2018 |language=Divehi |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190420110440/https://dho.mv/music/28773?ref=mhr-home |url-status=live |archivedate=20 April 2019 |accessdate=3 December 2018}}</ref> |- | 2009 !scope="row"| ''[[Mihithah Loabi Dheyshey]]'' | Jaufar | Recurring role | style="text-align: center;"| <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.muniavas.com/18666 |title=Additional cast of Huvaa |work=MuniAvas |last=Rasheed |first=Ahmed |date=12 November 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107104011/https://www.muniavas.com/18666 |url-status=live|archivedate=20 August 2020 |accessdate=20 August 2020 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- |}
