avas.com/18666 |title=Additional cast of Huvaa |work=MuniAvas |last=Rasheed |first=Ahmed |date=12 November 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107104011/https://www.muniavas.com/18666 |url-status=live|archivedate=20 August 2020 |access-date=20 August 2020 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- | 2021 !scope="row"| ''[[Aharenves Loabivey]]'' | Seytu | Main role (season 2); 7 episodes | style="text-align: center;"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.muniavas.com/13544 |title=Aharenves Loabivey: A love story by Emboo releases on Baiskoafu |work=MuniAvas |language=Divehi |last=Ajuwan |first=Ali |date=9 May 2019 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190608170804/https://www.muniavas.com/13544 |url-status=live |archivedate=8 June 2019 |access-date=11 May 2019 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- | {{TBA}} !scope="row"| ''Rimsha'' | | | |}
